      "text": "ふふ、とっても可愛いですね。今、SNSでも\nこういうフィルター流行っていますもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふふ、とっても可愛いですね。今、SNSでも\nこういうフィルター流行っていますもんね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2333363216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.1333363216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　沙季ちゃんも一緒にやろうよ～！\nほらほら、並んで並んで～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうだ！　沙季ちゃんも一緒にやろうよ～！\nほらほら、並んで並んで～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1333363216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8000029882
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ありませんね、少しだけですよ？　へぇ……\n六十年後の自分、というフィルターもあるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "仕方ありませんね、少しだけですよ？　へぇ……\n六十年後の自分、というフィルターもあるんですね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8000029882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.1333363216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "面白そう～！　やってみよ！\nわー、沙季おばあちゃんだ～！　しわしわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "面白そう～！　やってみよ！\nわー、沙季おばあちゃんだ～！　しわしわ～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1333363216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.5163248274
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.0666655859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "も、もう、芽衣ちゃんもしわしわじゃないですか\nでも、今のフィルターって凄いんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "も、もう、芽衣ちゃんもしわしわじゃないですか\nでも、今のフィルターって凄いんですね……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0666655859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.0333322526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、このゾンビフィルターっていうの千紗ちゃんが\n好きそう～！　はい、次は沙季ちゃんが撮って～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あ、このゾンビフィルターっていうの千紗ちゃんが\n好きそう～！　はい、次は沙季ちゃんが撮って～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.0333322526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4666655859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_06-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "携帯少し借りますね。凄い、結構リアルなゾンビですね\n帰ったら千紗に教えてあげないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "携帯少し借りますね。凄い、結構リアルなゾンビですね\n帰ったら千紗に教えてあげないと",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4666655859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
